item.title: Dittenhafer Airways Status
item.description: As of 7:50am on Sunday, there are 312 FlyteNet enabled aircraft in flight. Of these, 92% are green, while 7% are yellow and less than 1% are red. N923JB has reported a new MPS related alert on it's recently completed flight and N11206 enroute from JFK to LAX has fewer users than usual.
